26","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/umar-fears\/","url_meta":{"origin":22629,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Umar afraid they take Allah\u2019s mercy for granted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGo out and announce to the people that whoever testifies there is no God but Allah will surely enter Paradise.\u201d I went out and was met by Umar ibn al-Khattab. Umar said, \u201cReturn to the Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28989,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/umar-burden-long-salat-lectures\/","url_meta":{"origin":22629,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Sermons: Do not burden people with long prayers, lectures","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubaydullah ibn \u2018Adi reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cO people, do not make Allah hateful to his servants.\u201d They said, \u201cHow is that? Allah correct you!\u201d Umar said, \u201cOne of you is an Imam and he prolongs the prayer for people until what is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","l